sequenceDiagram
  actor C as Client (C)
  actor S as Server (S)

  C -&gt;&gt; C: Step 1: Encrypt private data&lt;br&gt;$Enc(m)$
  C -&gt;&gt; S: Step 2: Send $Enc(m)$ to S
  C -&gt;&gt; S: Step 3: Send query $f()$ to S
  S -&gt;&gt; S: Step 4: Perform $Eval(f)$ on $Enc(m)$
  S -&gt;&gt; C: Step 5: Return $Enc(f(m))$
  C -&gt;&gt; C: Step 6: Computes $Dec(Enc(f(m))) = f(m)$, and recovers $f(m)$


 A simple client-server HE scenario, where C is Client and S is Server
